y two hunting permits will be issued through an auction and raffle, with proceeds supporting elk conservation. Wildlife officials say the population is now sustainable, while some local residents remain divided over whether hunting should begin.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/north-carolina-spent-25-years-rebuilding-an-elk-population-that-had-disappeared-from-the-state-in-2027-it-will-allow-its-first-limited-hunt-with-just-two-permits/articleshow/132606207.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/north-carolina-spent-25-years-rebuilding-an-elk-population-that-had-disappeared-from-the-state-in-2027-it-will-allow-its-first-limited-hunt-with-just-two-permits/articleshow/132606207.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-24T19:30:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132607023,imgsize-80650.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Google co-founder Sergey Brin turned his $450 million superyacht into a floating headquarters with an entire deck dedicated to work]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132606960.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/google-co-founder-sergey-brin-turned-his-450-million-superyacht-into-a-floating-headquarters-with-an-entire-deck-dedicated-to-work/articleshow/132606960.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/google-co-founder-sergey-brin-turned-his-450-million-superyacht-into-a-floating-headquarters-with-an-entire-deck-dedicated-to-work/articleshow/132606960.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-24T18:57:04+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg