tened future]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132604297.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/inside-tuvalu-this-tiny-island-nation-has-just-one-airline-almost-no-tourists-and-a-future-threatened-by-rising-seas/articleshow/132604297.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/inside-tuvalu-this-tiny-island-nation-has-just-one-airline-almost-no-tourists-and-a-future-threatened-by-rising-seas/articleshow/132604297.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-24T17:10:39+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132604297,imgsize-1392855.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Bangladesh President Mohammad Shahabuddin resigns ahead of Sheikh Hasina's planned return, reports of rift with govt]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132603622.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/bangladesh-president-mohammad-shahabuddin-resigns-ahead-of-sheikh-hasinas-planned-return-reports-of-rift-with-govt/articleshow/132603622.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/bangladesh-president-mohammad-shahabuddin-resigns-ahead-of-sheikh-hasinas-planned-return-reports-of-rift-with-govt/articleshow/132603622.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-24T16:41:18+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132603718,imgsize-86645.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by John Stuart Mill: 'A person may cause evil to others not only by his actions but by his inaction, and in either case he is justly accountable to them for the injury']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132604824.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Philosopher John Stuart Mill emphasized the importance of accountability for both actions and inaction. He argued that choosing not to intervene in situations that could prevent harm carries its own set of responsibilities. This principle is particularly relevant in instances of bullying, corruption, or injustice, where those with authority must acknowledge their complicity. Mill's insightful quote challenges us to embrace moral responsibility and reflect on the repercussions of our silence.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/quote-of-the-day-by-john-stuart-mill-a-person-may-cause-evil-to-others-not-only-by-his-actions-but-by-his-inaction-and-in-either-case-he-is-justly-accountable-to-them-for-the-injury/articleshow/132604824.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/quote-of-the-day-by-john-stuart-mill-a-person-may-cause-evil-to-others-not-only-by-his-actions-but-by-his-inaction-and-in-either-case-he-is-justly-accountable-to-them-for-the-injury/articleshow/132604824.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-24T17:31:50+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132604965,imgsize-51126.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[500-year-old place with 200 skeletons buried beneath it: Construction workers uncover it]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132603160.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/construction-workers-in-ghent-uncover-a-500-year-old-neighbourhood-with-200-skeletons-buried-beneath-it/articleshow/132603160.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/construction-workers-in-ghent-uncover-a-500-year-old-neighbourhood-with-200-skeletons-buried-beneath-it/articleshow/132603160.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-24T16:22:32+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132603160,imgsize-2272310.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Oprah Winfrey: 'If you look at what you have in life, you'll always have more. If you look at what you don't have in life, you'll never have enough']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132605084.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Oprah Winfrey emphasizes the profound impact of gratitude on our fulfillment in life. By centering our attention on what we possess, we cultivate a sense of satisfaction and contentment. In stark contrast, fixating on what's lacking breeds an endless cycle of dissatisfaction. In a world where constant comparison is prevalent, embracing our current situation while striving for future goals nurtures a healthier mindset.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/quote-of-the-day-by-oprah-winfrey-if-you-look-at-what-you-have-in-life-youll-always-have-more-if-you-look-at-what-you-dont-have-in-life-youll-never-have-enough/articleshow/132605084.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/quote-of-the-day-by-oprah-winfrey-if-you-look-at-what-you-have-in-life-youll-always-have-more-if-you-look-at-what-you-dont-have-in-life-youll-never-have-enough/articleshow/132605084.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-24T17:45:30+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Wo